source.name: Terminal Aerodrome Forecasts Data Access
source.description: The National Weather Service (NWS) Telecommunications Gateway provides current and recent Terminal Aerodrome Forecasts from around the world are available from the NWS ftp://tgftp.nws.noaa.gov/data/forecasts/taf. TAFs are available as individual forecasts or in cycle files. The information available here is represented in a meteorological code .
